            >+381 61 30 14 647</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary/80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"
